      <title>马来西亚2月CPI同比上涨1.8% 超预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysias-feb-cpi-rises-18-on-year-more-than-forecast-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政府周一公布的数据显示，马来西亚 2 月份消费者价格指数 (CPI) 较上年同期上涨 1.8%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysias-feb-cpi-rises-18-on-year-more-than-forecast-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 04:04:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾前总统马英九将第二次访华</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-taiwan-president-ma-make-second-trip-china-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾前总统马英九将于下月第二次访问中国，他的办公室周一表示，在台海局势持续紧张之际，他将率领学生团队进行为期 11 天的访问，访问北京等地。 。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-taiwan-president-ma-make-second-trip-china-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 03:21:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国医学教授加入抗议，减少实习时间</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-medical-professors-join-protests-reduce-hours-practice-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国医学教授表示，他们将从周一开始减少实习时间，以支持实习医生因政府提高医学院招生计划而罢工一个多月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-medical-professors-join-protests-reduce-hours-practice-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 03:17:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾部长挑战中国将海洋主权主张提交仲裁</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-defence-minister-dares-china-put-maritime-sovereignty-claim-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周末再次陷入僵局后，菲律宾国防部长周一挑战中国将其在南海的主权主张提交国际仲裁，但表示菲律宾不会就其立场做出让步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-defence-minister-dares-china-put-maritime-sovereignty-claim-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 02:47:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡前交通部长因贪污案面临8项新指控</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/singapore-ex-transport-minister-faces-8-new-charges-graft-case-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡反腐败机构称，新加坡前交通部长伊斯瓦兰周一在一起腐败案中又被提出八项指控，这是该城邦最引人注目的腐败丑闻之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/singapore-ex-transport-minister-faces-8-new-charges-graft-case-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 02:43:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国努力削减货币繁文缛节</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/south-koreas-efforts-cut-its-currency-red-tape-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国正在寻求提升其金融市场的全球形象，这也意味着放松对其货币韩元交易方式的一些严格限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/south-koreas-efforts-cut-its-currency-red-tape-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 02:17:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国推动市场全球化的努力受到外汇历史的困扰</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/south-koreas-push-make-its-markets-global-dogged-by-fx-history-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在韩国寻求提升其金融市场的全球形象之际，这个出口大国正在努力放松严格的货币限制，这些限制多年来一直是该国投资者和贸易商的主要痛点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/south-koreas-push-make-its-markets-global-dogged-by-fx-history-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 02:14:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市持平，美元因日本谨慎态度而受到抑制</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市周一出现波动，原因是投资者担心本周美国通胀数据可能会破坏降息前景，而日本的货币干预风险暂时阻止了日元的跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 00:27:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚建议最低工资与通货膨胀保持一致</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-recommend-minimum-wage-rise-line-with-inflation-2024-03-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于低收入家庭继续努力应对生活成本，澳大利亚政府今年将支持根据通货膨胀提高最低工资，尽管随着通货膨胀的缓解，涨幅将较小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-recommend-minimum-wage-rise-line-with-inflation-2024-03-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 23:11:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
